Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.40,0:00:07.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Astro Boy
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.21,0:00:10.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Over the sky, la-la-la
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.99,0:00:13.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Beyond the stars
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.62,0:00:17.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's go, Atom
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.21,0:00:21.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Until the jet limit
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.04,0:00:25.01,Default,,0,0,0,,A heart-warming la-la-la
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.01,0:00:27.58,Default,,0,0,0,,The child of science
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.58,0:00:31.51,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a million-horsepower engine
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.51,0:00:35.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Mighty Atom
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.48,0:00:42.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Listen carefully, la-la-la
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.50,0:00:45.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Open your eyes wide
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.15,0:00:48.62,Default,,0,0,0,,That's right, Atom
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.62,0:00:52.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't be off your guard
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.80,0:00:56.51,Default,,0,0,0,,A righteous la-la-la
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.51,0:00:59.15,Default,,0,0,0,,The child of science
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.15,0:01:03.10,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a seven-force power
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.10,0:01:07.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Mighty Atom
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.11,0:01:33.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, it quieted down.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.43,0:01:37.09,Default,,0,0,0,,So scary. I can't sleep like this every night.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.09,0:01:41.50,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm going to move tomorrow!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.50,0:01:44.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you going to abandon your ancestor's land? I'm not going to!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.72,0:01:48.68,Default,,0,0,0,,That's right! As long as the Inmen Jiwa doesn't move, this town's safe!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.20,0:01:50.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Inmen Jiwa.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.82,0:01:56.54,Default,,0,0,0,,What is that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.87,0:01:59.04,Default,,0,0,0,,It's will-o'-the-wisp!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.80,0:02:08.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Inmen Jiwa
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.03,0:02:12.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Everyone, please take a look at your left side.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.04,0:02:15.75,Default,,0,0,0,,What you can see on the mountain is called Inmen Jiwa.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.75,0:02:19.85,Default,,0,0,0,,It became like that by weathering.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.85,0:02:22.55,Default,,0,0,0,,That's a weird rock. It looks like someone.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.55,0:02:23.80,Default,,0,0,0,,It looks like Shibukaki.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.95,0:02:28.77,Default,,0,0,0,,A long time ago, there were many legends that said
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.77,0:02:30.83,Default,,0,0,0,,that it's possessed or it was made by the devil...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.83,0:02:34.02,Default,,0,0,0,,No one believes in such superstition anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.40,0:02:37.08,Default,,0,0,0,,However! There is one legend that
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.08,0:02:39.88,Default,,0,0,0,,everyone in this town believes until today.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.88,0:02:44.86,Default,,0,0,0,,The legend says that if Inmen Jiwa, facing east,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.86,0:02:48.88,Default,,0,0,0,,turns away to where the lake is, the town of Sparitz will perish.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.88,0:02:52.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Ridiculous. A rock wouldn't move by itself. Right, Atom?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.59,0:02:57.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? Is that a removal van?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.23,0:02:59.50,Default,,0,0,0,,That's strange.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.50,0:03:03.74,Default,,0,0,0,,It feels like the direction has changed a bit from 20 years ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.92,0:03:06.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Next is Sparitz.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.61,0:03:09.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Teacher, we are getting off at Sparitz, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.13,0:03:11.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes. Get ready.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.39,0:03:13.59,Default,,0,0,0,,We are finally here. Yay!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.19,0:03:21.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Mr.Shunsaku.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.08,0:03:26.17,Default,,0,0,0,,-Welcome. -It's been 10 years.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.17,0:03:29.21,Default,,0,0,0,,So you guys are Atom and Uran?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.21,0:03:32.37,Default,,0,0,0,,He's my old colleague, Goro Yamakawa.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.37,0:03:33.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Nice to meet you!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.45,0:03:34.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Welcome.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.27,0:03:39.77,Default,,0,0,0,,I see... There are that many earthquakes?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.77,0:03:41.47,Default,,0,0,0,,This town is over now.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.47,0:03:45.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Fields are getting dried up, cliffs are collapsing, and huts are crumbling as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.67,0:03:48.92,Default,,0,0,0,,So everyone is abandoning this town to move away?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.92,0:03:54.11,Default,,0,0,0,,There have been almost 100 earthquakes ever since I got here as a Japanese teacher.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.11,0:03:58.29,Default,,0,0,0,,It feels like the Inmen Jiwa has shifted a little.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.91,0:04:07.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Teacher, welcome.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.52,0:04:10.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Mr.Shunsaku. This is Dr.Archie, archaeologist.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.86,0:04:15.74,Default,,0,0,0,,He's staying here to study the ancient German ruins.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.74,0:04:20.22,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm Shunsaku Ban. Guten Morgen. This is Atom and Uran.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.22,0:04:21.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Nice to meet you!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.27,0:04:23.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Guten Morgen.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.47,0:04:25.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Would you like a cup of tea?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.19,0:04:27.76,Default,,0,0,0,,No, thank you. I have to go investigate.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.88,0:04:29.64,Default,,0,0,0,,He's weird.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.64,0:04:34.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Watch your mouth. Every scholar is bit eccentric.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.06,0:04:37.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Teacher, I'm going to go see the Inmen Jiwa. Is that all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.85,0:04:39.45,Default,,0,0,0,,-All right. -Me too!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.45,0:04:41.80,Default,,0,0,0,,No. I'm going to fly.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.80,0:04:43.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Take me.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.41,0:04:45.29,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll tell you about it after I see it.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.47,0:04:48.78,Default,,0,0,0,,You are mean.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.09,0:04:54.62,Default,,0,0,0,,It looks really heavy and hard.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.91,0:04:57.70,Default,,0,0,0,,It might be a meteor.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.00,0:05:01.92,Default,,0,0,0,,This rock did move, as expected.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.37,0:05:05.12,Default,,0,0,0,,It's because of those earthquakes Mr.Yamakawa talked about.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.79,0:05:06.85,Default,,0,0,0,,However,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.85,0:05:10.19,Default,,0,0,0,,there's no way we will be able to see the other side of this rock.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.80,0:05:11.65,Default,,0,0,0,,It's just my imagination.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.64,0:05:17.79,Default,,0,0,0,,The mountain-
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.79,0:05:22.98,Default,,0,0,0,,This is heaven. It feels like I'm in one of hot springs in Japan.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.40,0:05:27.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Little bit of salt, sulfur and calcium.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.40,0:05:30.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Is this supposed to feel that much great?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.11,0:05:32.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Teacher, would you like to play the diving game?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.45,0:05:34.36,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't want to dive.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.36,0:05:38.11,Default,,0,0,0,,-Then let's get out. -You don't like hot springs?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.60,0:05:41.35,Default,,0,0,0,,It's difficult to clean myself if sulfur gets accumulated.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.35,0:05:44.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Robots are so inconvenient.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.45,0:05:48.17,Default,,0,0,0,,It's here!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.52,0:05:51.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? I thought you didn't want to dive in.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.02,0:05:52.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Will-o'-the-wisp!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.80,0:05:53.84,Default,,0,0,0,,What? Oh!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.98,0:05:56.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.02,0:06:00.03,Default,,0,0,0,,It's here! Here! Here!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.71,0:06:03.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Who are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.71,0:06:11.74,Default,,0,0,0,,What is that? It's like a bomb.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.74,0:06:12.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Shoot!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.04,0:06:15.02,Default,,0,0,0,,This time for sure!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.25,0:06:19.27,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not going to let you go no matter what.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.66,0:06:24.83,Default,,0,0,0,,I lost it.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.01,0:06:37.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Earthquake!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.72,0:06:40.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Atom, get up. Uran, it's an earthquake.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.73,0:06:46.36,Default,,0,0,0,,-This is big. -Would the other teacher be okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.36,0:06:48.73,Default,,0,0,0,,-I'll go and check. Take care of Uran. -Yes, sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.23,0:06:51.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Neighbor! Dr.Archie!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.37,0:06:54.70,Default,,0,0,0,,It stopped.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.70,0:06:55.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Ouch!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.15,0:06:58.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Doctor! Dr.Archie.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.22,0:07:00.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you all right? Doctor...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.25,0:07:08.94,Default,,0,0,0,,He's not here. Where did he go in the middle of night?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.13,0:07:18.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you running away in the end?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.29,0:07:20.61,Default,,0,0,0,,There is a crack in the middle of my house.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.61,0:07:23.37,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm scared. It's so scary.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.37,0:07:28.35,Default,,0,0,0,,If the dam gets a crack or something, the whole town will be flooded.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.15,0:07:40.05,Default,,0,0,0,,-I'm not scared at all. -Whatever, you were sleeping.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.05,0:07:42.42,Default,,0,0,0,,It was fun, rocking like a ship.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.42,0:07:44.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Uran, you are so easygoing.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.27,0:07:46.09,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not the right time to fool around.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.09,0:07:48.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Everyone's having a hard time because of earthquakes.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.98,0:07:52.42,Default,,0,0,0,,You are doing it again. You are such a nagger.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.42,0:07:54.38,Default,,0,0,0,,-Where are you going? -Why would you care?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.38,0:07:56.19,Default,,0,0,0,,She's always like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.23,0:07:59.56,Default,,0,0,0,,-Ah, Doctor. -Hello.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.56,0:08:02.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Doctor, where were you last night?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.12,0:08:04.40,Default,,0,0,0,,I took a walk because I couldn't sleep.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.40,0:08:06.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Walk...?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.32,0:08:11.84,Default,,0,0,0,,That red dirt on that shirt is...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.84,0:08:13.94,Default,,0,0,0,,It looks the same as the Inmen Jiwa's red dirt.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.12,0:08:16.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Teacher, you are back.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.84,0:08:18.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Have you heard about it?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.53,0:08:23.29,Default,,0,0,0,,The government research team is getting here tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.29,0:08:24.65,Default,,0,0,0,,A research team?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.65,0:08:28.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes. They are going to figure out the cause of frequent earthquakes or something.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.00,0:08:31.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, then. I'm going to get some sleep.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.10,0:08:40.63,Default,,0,0,0,,This is bellflower, this is cosmea.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.08,0:08:45.71,Default,,0,0,0,,That's... This... What is this?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.71,0:08:46.60,Default,,0,0,0,,That's Chinese pink!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.15,0:08:53.69,Default,,0,0,0,,-This is madder. This is... -Tuberose!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.27,0:08:55.99,Default,,0,0,0,,My name is Uran!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.99,0:08:57.86,Default,,0,0,0,,My brother is Atom!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.86,0:08:59.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Your name is?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.22,0:09:03.87,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm the will-o'-the-wisp boy.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.87,0:09:07.98,Default,,0,0,0,,-You know a lot. -I know everything about the mountain.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.98,0:09:09.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Where are you from?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.17,0:09:11.33,Default,,0,0,0,,From a faraway mountain.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.88,0:09:13.56,Default,,0,0,0,,What were you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.56,0:09:16.17,Default,,0,0,0,,I was digging holes day and night.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.17,0:09:19.55,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm so tired. People can be annoying.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.10,0:09:23.33,Default,,0,0,0,,They've never treated you nicely, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.33,0:09:24.98,Default,,0,0,0,,There's no such thing as a warm person in this world.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.98,0:09:26.11,Default,,0,0,0,,There is.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.11,0:09:29.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's go to the town. I'll introduce you to Mr.Beard.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.91,0:09:32.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Please keep it secret that you've met me.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.35,0:09:33.71,Default,,0,0,0,,How come?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.71,0:09:35.87,Default,,0,0,0,,If you do, I'll show you something great.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.87,0:09:37.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Then, I will.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.15,0:09:38.73,Default,,0,0,0,,All right, here.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.53,0:09:43.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Two wires are here!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.31,0:09:47.41,Default,,0,0,0,,From these two wires...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.41,0:09:49.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Fireworks!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.76,0:09:51.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Wow, that's amazing.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.54,0:09:55.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Spring, March. Weeping willows!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.53,0:09:56.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Great!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.17,0:10:02.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Look at that. The crack gets bigger as we get closer to the Inmen Jiwa mountain.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.22,0:10:07.68,Default,,0,0,0,,So the area near Inmen Jiwa is in trouble.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.08,0:10:13.23,Default,,0,0,0,,I see! That's why Inmen Jiwa is shifting. I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.44,0:10:16.56,Default,,0,0,0,,-Hey, I want to try making fireworks. -All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.90,0:10:18.70,Default,,0,0,0,,But you have to be careful.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.62,0:10:22.69,Default,,0,0,0,,So these have to touch each other, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.37,0:10:26.91,Default,,0,0,0,,What was that sound?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.91,0:10:28.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Teacher, I'll go and look.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.75,0:10:31.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Uran, wake up.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.05,0:10:34.35,Default,,0,0,0,,-I told you to be careful. -Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.29,0:10:36.89,Default,,0,0,0,,What did you do to my sister?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.89,0:10:37.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Atom...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.88,0:10:39.82,Default,,0,0,0,,I won't forgive you if you bother her!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.90,0:10:42.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.73,0:10:45.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Atom, it was my fault.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.39,0:10:47.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't do that to him!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.68,0:10:50.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey! Atom!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.19,0:10:52.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Atom!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.43,0:10:55.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? What was it? There's no one.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.11,0:11:04.62,Default,,0,0,0,,As expected, there is a trace that Inmen Jiwa has shifted.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.41,0:11:08.52,Default,,0,0,0,,This dirt is...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.87,0:11:12.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Shoot.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.61,0:11:18.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.93,0:11:27.65,Default,,0,0,0,,So last night's will-o'-the-wisp was that one.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.65,0:11:28.41,Default,,0,0,0,,All right!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.27,0:11:32.79,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm going to get you today for sure!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.91,0:11:35.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Shoot. I lost it.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.19,0:11:38.84,Default,,0,0,0,,I found it!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.33,0:11:41.37,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not this one.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.97,0:11:46.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Over there... Shoot.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.49,0:11:48.51,Default,,0,0,0,,This time for sure!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.92,0:11:51.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Gotcha!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.84,0:11:53.45,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.26,0:11:57.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Hold on!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.79,0:12:00.73,Default,,0,0,0,,I lost it again.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.56,0:12:04.27,Default,,0,0,0,,This area looks familiar.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.27,0:12:07.07,Default,,0,0,0,,It did disappear around here last time.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.78,0:12:17.93,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a castle.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.54,0:12:21.61,Default,,0,0,0,,I see. This is an old castle from a long time ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.61,0:12:23.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Earthquake again!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.96,0:12:42.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Teacher.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.99,0:12:45.01,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm tired.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.01,0:12:46.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't slack off!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.45,0:12:48.47,Default,,0,0,0,,I must be running out of energy.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.47,0:12:52.59,Default,,0,0,0,,We have to find that treasure chamber today no matter what.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.95,0:12:56.08,Default,,0,0,0,,There are suspicious visitors around and government workers are coming as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.08,0:12:58.53,Default,,0,0,0,,What in the world is in this mountain?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.53,0:13:01.22,Default,,0,0,0,,It's something great you cannot even imagine.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.22,0:13:03.69,Default,,0,0,0,,As I was studying the history of the Vikings,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.69,0:13:07.42,Default,,0,0,0,,I found out that their treasure is buried under this castle.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.36,0:13:12.72,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know what it is, but there is a rock with carved letters in this hole as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.28,0:13:14.86,Default,,0,0,0,,What? A rock with carved letters?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.00,0:13:19.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Give me the lamp.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.30,0:13:28.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Here. They are ancient Scandinavian scripts.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.10,0:13:35.44,Default,,0,0,0,,All right, Will-o'-the-wisp. Smash this rock!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.44,0:13:39.22,Default,,0,0,0,,That rock is very hard. My drill won't work.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.38,0:13:42.65,Default,,0,0,0,,All right, turn around. I'll change your energy.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.88,0:13:47.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Now your energy is 200 times higher.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.40,0:13:51.32,Default,,0,0,0,,With that, you will be able to tear any rock down.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.32,0:13:53.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Wouldn't a huge earthquake occur if I do such thing?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.65,0:13:56.51,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't care. Do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.51,0:13:58.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Here I come, treasure!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.90,0:14:13.52,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't feel anything unusual.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.52,0:14:15.96,Default,,0,0,0,,-Atom! -Ah, it's Uran.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.61,0:14:20.37,Default,,0,0,0,,-Uran! Over here. -Atom.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.36,0:14:31.58,Default,,0,0,0,,I see. So that Will-o'-the-wisp disappeared here.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.58,0:14:32.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, Uran.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.90,0:14:35.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Who is it? Whose robot is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.24,0:14:37.59,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.00,0:14:39.33,Default,,0,0,0,,You are hiding something, Uran.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.33,0:14:42.76,Default,,0,0,0,,-I promised to not tell anything. -He's a bad one.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.76,0:14:45.98,Default,,0,0,0,,He turns into a wil-o'-the-wisp every night and surprises townspeople.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.98,0:14:49.71,Default,,0,0,0,,He's not a bad one. He's just got little problems.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.71,0:14:50.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Uran!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.10,0:14:54.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Will-o'-the-wisp is my friend!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.73,0:14:57.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Atom, this rock's moving!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.64,0:14:59.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? Rock?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.70,0:15:01.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Look. Here. You see?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.41,0:15:07.53,Default,,0,0,0,,That kind of device was...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.01,0:15:11.84,Default,,0,0,0,,It's like a magic. Atom, let's go in.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.84,0:15:12.62,Default,,0,0,0,,All right!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.93,0:15:26.01,Default,,0,0,0,,What was that explosion right now?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.01,0:15:27.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Help!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.10,0:15:31.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Help!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.47,0:15:34.23,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm going to be buried!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.01,0:15:38.18,Default,,0,0,0,,-The Inmen Jiwa is...! -It's facing the dam!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.18,0:15:41.15,Default,,0,0,0,,-It's a curse. -Something scary will happen!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.02,0:15:44.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Help!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.02,0:15:45.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Teacher!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.87,0:15:48.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Teacher, what happened?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.98,0:15:53.75,Default,,0,0,0,,While I was investigating the Inmen Jiwa, something exploded from the back.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.75,0:15:57.07,Default,,0,0,0,,This is a crime. Let's inform the people in town!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.74,0:16:05.51,Default,,0,0,0,,I finally found it. This is the treasure of the Vikings!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.88,0:16:17.64,Default,,0,0,0,,-Teacher, Inmen Jiwa is sliding down the mountain. -Stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.64,0:16:20.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Inmen Jiwa! Where are you going?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.69,0:16:26.80,Default,,0,0,0,,-Atom, stop it. -Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.86,0:16:34.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Atom!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.21,0:16:41.59,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a heavy rock. Hurry...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.82,0:16:45.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Hurry...! Everyone, run...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.44,0:16:48.63,Default,,0,0,0,,-Go, Atom! -Teacher, I'm scared.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.63,0:16:50.63,Default,,0,0,0,,It's like that rock's alive.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.47,0:16:58.17,Default,,0,0,0,,It looks like it's heading to the dam with a purpose.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.24,0:17:04.64,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm losing my energy...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.79,0:17:10.77,Default,,0,0,0,,No more...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.82,0:17:15.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Atom!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.37,0:17:17.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Atom, run! You will be crushed!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.47,0:17:28.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Inmen Jiwa.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.72,0:17:41.21,Default,,0,0,0,,The town...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.21,0:17:42.24,Default,,0,0,0,,will sink underwater.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.90,0:17:47.39,Default,,0,0,0,,That's right!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.39,0:17:50.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Dr.Archie might be underground!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.26,0:17:51.32,Default,,0,0,0,,We have to save him!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.31,0:17:53.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Atom!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.69,0:17:57.12,Default,,0,0,0,,-Where are you going? -Atom's almost out of his energy...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.04,0:18:02.91,Default,,0,0,0,,-What is that sound? -Teacher, look at that.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.59,0:18:05.26,Default,,0,0,0,,There are strange letters again.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.26,0:18:06.34,Default,,0,0,0,,What? Letters?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.10,0:18:12.12,Default,,0,0,0,,"If anyone interrupts the King's sleep, he will be cursed.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.12,0:18:17.21,Default,,0,0,0,,The patron of this tomb, Inmen Jiwa, will take his life."
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.21,0:18:18.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Oops!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.00,0:18:20.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Now you can't get out of here.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.55,0:18:24.64,Default,,0,0,0,,-You were trying to steal this treasure, right? -You, Will-o'-the-wisp...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.16,0:18:40.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Will-o'-the-wisp!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.38,0:18:42.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Make a hole on the ceiling with your drill.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.99,0:18:44.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Get me out of here right now!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.99,0:18:47.01,Default,,0,0,0,,-No! -What?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.01,0:18:50.50,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't like you anymore. You are always ordering me around.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.50,0:18:53.32,Default,,0,0,0,,What? You are my assistant.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.58,0:18:55.72,Default,,0,0,0,,You were just using my power.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.72,0:18:57.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Dr.Archie!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.90,0:18:59.94,Default,,0,0,0,,You are...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.94,0:19:01.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Doctor. You were here.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.83,0:19:04.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Help. Get me out of here.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.26,0:19:05.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Take my hand...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.97,0:19:09.64,Default,,0,0,0,,No, I can't...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.64,0:19:10.97,Default,,0,0,0,,I have no energy.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.90,0:19:15.35,Default,,0,0,0,,-Atom! Leave him! -Will-o'-the-wisp.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.35,0:19:18.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Were you there? Please help me.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.23,0:19:21.34,Default,,0,0,0,,No. I don't have much energy either.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.34,0:19:24.18,Default,,0,0,0,,We can survive if we work together.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.18,0:19:26.25,Default,,0,0,0,,No thanks. Bye!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.25,0:19:27.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Will-o'-the-wisp.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.37,0:19:29.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Please. Wait.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.19,0:19:32.89,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm losing it...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.96,0:19:42.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Atom!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.82,0:19:44.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Atom!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.65,0:19:46.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Atom...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.13,0:19:49.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Atom!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.00,0:19:53.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Atom, my precious Atom. He drowned to death.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.89,0:19:58.41,Default,,0,0,0,,I had to stop him. He was running out of his energy.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.96,0:20:01.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Atom!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.96,0:20:03.36,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll go and rescue him.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.36,0:20:04.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Wh, wh, wh, what?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.90,0:20:08.81,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm going to go rescue Atom and the doctor. That's what robots do!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.81,0:20:10.51,Default,,0,0,0,,You can't! Stop there!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.38,0:20:17.37,Default,,0,0,0,,What, Will-o'-the-wisp.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.69,0:20:19.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Leave it to me, Uran.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.96,0:20:23.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Will-o'-the-wisp!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.61,0:20:29.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Atom, I'm sorry to get you involved.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.35,0:20:30.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Doctor,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.50,0:20:43.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Teacher! Atom. I'll get you out.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.28,0:20:48.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Atom! Atom. My son.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.79,0:20:51.46,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm glad. I'm so glad.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.75,0:20:54.20,Default,,0,0,0,,You have to thank him.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.50,0:20:58.45,Default,,0,0,0,,-That's right! Where is he? -Over there.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.95,0:21:02.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Will-o'-the-wisp! Everyone wants to thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.50,0:21:04.00,Default,,0,0,0,,It's all right.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.00,0:21:06.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Rather than that... Give this to your brother.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.76,0:21:09.23,Default,,0,0,0,,-What is this? -It's energy cassette.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.23,0:21:12.39,Default,,0,0,0,,-Huh? Thank you, Will-o'-the-wisp. -Well, then.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.39,0:21:14.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? Where are you going?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.64,0:21:16.49,Default,,0,0,0,,No! Don't go!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.49,0:21:19.10,Default,,0,0,0,,We will meet again sometime for sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.07,0:21:22.43,Default,,0,0,0,,-Bye! -Will-o'-the-wisp!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.57,0:21:26.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Will-o'-the-wisp!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.00,0:21:38.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.37,0:21:43.14,Default,,0,0,0,,It's here. That's the real rescue ship.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.37,0:21:59.46,Default,,0,0,0,,-You look satisfied. -We kept the treasure.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.46,0:22:03.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Now the treasure of the Vikings will be down there forever.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.20,0:22:05.19,Default,,0,0,0,,No one can take it.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.59,0:22:08.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Good bye, Inmen Jiwa.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.28,0:22:31.64,Default,,0,0,0,,A funny and peculiar robot found in the park.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.64,0:22:35.51,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not trying to part from Uran.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.51,0:22:38.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Uran's in trouble!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.09,0:22:42.85,Default,,0,0,0,,And I got attacked by the assassin Lamp, who goes only after robots.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.27,0:22:47.09,Default,,0,0,0,,And Uran falls in love with the handsome robot Zeus!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.09,0:22:49.58,Default,,0,0,0,,But the real aspect of Zeus is...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.23,0:22:56.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Next on Astro Boy, "Uran Loves Hitman"
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.07,0:23:10.08,Default,,0,0,0,,My arms and legs
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.08,0:23:13.60,Default,,0,0,0,,fly over the sky with a jet
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.60,0:23:17.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Astro Boy
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.71,0:23:20.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Mighty Atom
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.47,0:23:24.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Inside my waist,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.42,0:23:27.94,Default,,0,0,0,,a machine gun's light
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.94,0:23:32.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Astro Boy
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.06,0:23:35.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Mighty Atom
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.22,0:23:38.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Searchlight's eyes
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.90,0:23:42.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Laser Blast's hands
Dialogue: 0,0:23:42.47,0:23:49.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Seven powers, Wa Wa Wa Wa
Dialogue: 0,0:23:49.69,0:23:55.95,Default,,0,0,0,,We fight for the peace
Dialogue: 0,0:23:55.95,0:24:03.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Come on, let's go together
